requests: select  cir.name  as CIRCLENAME , u.username,r.team||'-'||r.rolename as PROFILE, to_date(to_char(u.createdTime, 'dd-MM-yyyy'), 'dd-MM-yyyy')  as CREATIONDATE  from Users u  join userroles ur on ur.userid_ck = u.userid_pk inner join roles r on ur.roleid_ck = r.roleid_pk inner join circles cir on u.circleid_fk=cir.circleid_pk where  u.username not in (select u.username  from users u  inner join (select distinct usersid_fk,trunc(auditdate)auddate from audits  where TO_CHAR (auditdate, 'DY', 'NLS_DATE_LANGUAGE=ENGLISH') NOT IN ('SUN') and  to_date(to_char(auditdate,'DD/MM/YYYY'),'DD/MM/YYYY')   BETWEEN TO_DATE(to_char(sysdate-8, 'DD/MM/YYYY '),'DD/MM/YYYY')   AND TO_DATE(to_char(sysdate-1, 'DD/MM/YYYY'),'DD/MM/YYYY') and auditActionName='LOGIN')x  on x.USERSID_FK=u.userid_pk inner join userroles ur on u.userid_pk=ur.userid_ck inner join roles r on r.roleid_pk=ur.roleid_ck inner join circles cir on cir.circleid_pk=u.circleid_fk where r.levelType  not in ('NHQ','SUPER_ADMIN','ZONE')  and r.team not in('QA','GeoBond','Samsung','Business')  and r.roleId_PK !=314 and u.deleted=0  and u.enabled=1   and u.isjcp=1  and TO_CHAR (x.auddate, 'DY', 'NLS_DATE_LANGUAGE=ENGLISH') NOT IN ('SUN')  and  to_date(to_char(x.auddate,'DD/MM/YYYY'),'DD/MM/YYYY') BETWEEN TO_DATE(to_char(sysdate-8, 'DD/MM/YYYY '),'DD/MM/YYYY')  AND TO_DATE(to_char(sysdate-1, 'DD/MM/YYYY'),'DD/MM/YYYY')  group by u.username, cir.name ,r.team||'-'||r.rolename,  to_date(to_char(u.createdTime, 'dd-MM-yyyy'), 'dd-MM-yyyy')  having count(x.auddate) >=3) and u.isjcp=1 and u.deleted=0 and u.enabled=1 and  r.levelType not in ('NHQ','SUPER_ADMIN','ZONE')   and r.team not in('QA','GeoBond','Samsung','Business') and r.roleId_PK !=314 order by cir.name

requests: select y.CIRCLENAME,count(*) from  (select u.USERID_PK ,initcap(cir.name) as CIRCLENAME from users u  inner join (select distinct usersid_fk,trunc(auditdate)auddate from audits  where TO_CHAR (auditdate, 'DY', 'NLS_DATE_LANGUAGE=ENGLISH') NOT IN ('SUN')  and  to_date(to_char(auditdate,'DD/MM/YYYY'),'DD/MM/YYYY')  BETWEEN TO_DATE(to_char(sysdate-8, 'DD/MM/YYYY '),'DD/MM/YYYY')  AND TO_DATE(to_char(sysdate-1, 'DD/MM/YYYY'),'DD/MM/YYYY')  and auditActionName='LOGIN')x on x.USERSID_FK=u.userid_pk inner join userroles ur on u.userid_pk=ur.userid_ck  inner join roles r on r.roleid_pk=ur.roleid_ck inner join circles cir on cir.circleid_pk=u.circleid_fk where r.levelType  not in ('NHQ','SUPER_ADMIN','ZONE')  and r.team not in('QA','GeoBond','Samsung','Business')  and u.deleted=0  and u.enabled=1   and u.isjcp=1  and TO_CHAR (x.auddate, 'DY', 'NLS_DATE_LANGUAGE=ENGLISH') NOT IN ('SUN')  and  to_date(to_char(x.auddate,'DD/MM/YYYY'),'DD/MM/YYYY') BETWEEN TO_DATE(to_char(sysdate-8, 'DD/MM/YYYY '),'DD/MM/YYYY')  AND TO_DATE(to_char(sysdate-1, 'DD/MM/YYYY'),'DD/MM/YYYY') group by u.userid_pk, initcap(cir.name) ,r.team||'-'||r.rolename, to_date(to_char(u.createdTime, 'dd-MM-yyyy'), 'dd-MM-yyyy')  having count(x.auddate) >=3 )y group by y.CIRCLENAME order by y.CIRCLENAME

requests: select y.CIRCLENAME,count(*)  from (select u.USERID_PK ,cir.name as CIRCLENAME from users u inner join  (select distinct usersid_fk,trunc(auditdate)auddate from audits  where TO_CHAR (auditdate, 'DY', 'NLS_DATE_LANGUAGE=ENGLISH') NOT IN ('SUN') and  to_date(to_char(auditdate,'DD/MM/YYYY'),'DD/MM/YYYY') BETWEEN TO_DATE(to_char(sysdate-8, 'DD/MM/YYYY '),'DD/MM/YYYY')  AND TO_DATE(to_char(sysdate-1, 'DD/MM/YYYY'),'DD/MM/YYYY')  and auditActionName='LOGIN')x on x.USERSID_FK=u.userid_pk  inner join userroles ur on u.userid_pk=ur.userid_ck  inner join roles r on r.roleid_pk=ur.roleid_ck   inner join TEAM team on team.TEAMID_PK=r.teamId_fk inner join circles cir on cir.circleid_pk=u.circleid_fk  inner join zones z on z.zoneid_pk=cir.zoneid_fk where upper(z.name)=upper(?) and  r.levelType  not in ('NHQ','SUPER_ADMIN','ZONE')  and r.team not in('QA','GeoBond','Samsung','Business')  and r.roleId_PK !=314 and u.deleted=0 and u.enabled=1 and u.isjcp=1  and TO_CHAR (x.auddate, 'DY', 'NLS_DATE_LANGUAGE=ENGLISH') NOT IN ('SUN') and  to_date(to_char(x.auddate,'DD/MM/YYYY'),'DD/MM/YYYY') BETWEEN TO_DATE(to_char(sysdate-8, 'DD/MM/YYYY '),'DD/MM/YYYY') AND TO_DATE(to_char(sysdate-1, 'DD/MM/YYYY'),'DD/MM/YYYY') group by u.userid_pk, cir.name ,team.NAME||'-'||r.rolename, to_date(to_char(u.createdTime, 'dd-MM-yyyy'), 'dd-MM-yyyy')  having count(x.auddate) >=3 ) y group by y.CIRCLENAME order by 1

requests: select  cir.name  as CIRCLENAME , u.username,team.NAME||'-'||r.rolename as PROFILE,  to_date(to_char(u.createdTime, 'dd-MM-yyyy'), 'dd-MM-yyyy')  as CREATIONDATE  from Users u  join userroles ur on ur.userid_ck = u.userid_pk   inner join roles r on ur.roleid_ck = r.roleid_pk  inner join TEAM team on team.TEAMID_PK=r.teamId_fk  inner join circles cir on u.circleid_fk=cir.circleid_pk where  u.username not in (select u.username  from users u   inner join (select distinct usersid_fk,trunc(auditdate)auddate from audits   where TO_CHAR (auditdate, 'DY', 'NLS_DATE_LANGUAGE=ENGLISH') NOT IN ('SUN') and   to_date(to_char(auditdate,'DD/MM/YYYY'),'DD/MM/YYYY')   BETWEEN TO_DATE(to_char(sysdate-8, 'DD/MM/YYYY '),'DD/MM/YYYY')   AND TO_DATE(to_char(sysdate-1, 'DD/MM/YYYY'),'DD/MM/YYYY') and auditActionName='LOGIN')x  on x.USERSID_FK=u.userid_pk  inner join userroles ur on u.userid_pk=ur.userid_ck inner join roles r on r.roleid_pk=ur.roleid_ck  inner join TEAM team on team.TEAMID_PK=r.teamId_fk  inner join circles cir on cir.circleid_pk=u.circleid_fk  where r.levelType  not in ('NHQ','SUPER_ADMIN','ZONE')  and r.team not in('QA','GeoBond','Samsung','Business')   and r.roleId_PK !=314 and u.deleted=0  and u.enabled=1   and u.isjcp=1   and  TO_CHAR (x.auddate, 'DY', 'NLS_DATE_LANGUAGE=ENGLISH') NOT IN ('SUN')  and   to_date(to_char(x.auddate,'DD/MM/YYYY'),'DD/MM/YYYY') BETWEEN TO_DATE(to_char(sysdate-8, 'DD/MM/YYYY '),'DD/MM/YYYY')  AND TO_DATE(to_char(sysdate-1, 'DD/MM/YYYY'),'DD/MM/YYYY')  group by u.username, cir.name ,team.NAME||'-'||r.rolename,  to_date(to_char(u.createdTime, 'dd-MM-yyyy'), 'dd-MM-yyyy')  having count(x.auddate) >=3) and u.isjcp=1 and u.deleted=0  and u.enabled=1 and  r.levelType not in ('NHQ','SUPER_ADMIN','ZONE')   and r.team not in('QA','GeoBond','Samsung','Business')  and r.roleId_PK !=314 order by cir.name
